description:
Join thousands of #cloudnative professionals, developers, and #opensource advocates to advance the future of #k8s and cloud technology. From sharing best practices to tackling real-world challenges, KubeCon + CloudNativeCon is the ultimate platform for learning, networking, and development. Don’t miss out and be part of the community this November 12-15 in Salt Lake City!

Event details: https://events.linuxfoundation.org/kubecon-cloudnativecon-north-america/

#kubecon #cloudnativecon #opensource
title: Empowering Diversity and Collaboration at #Kubecon + #cloudnativecon
